snippet.title: Pokémon Saiph - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
My Pokémon game, Pokémon Saiph has finally been released!

Where you can get the game itself:
https://www.pokecommunity.com/showthread.php?p=10017332#post10017332

Thank you all for the support! ^^
